        DYNAMIC RESULT SETS 2
        LANGUAGE SQL
        SPECIFIC SUMITG1.DTPROC3
        NOT DETERMINISTIC
        MODIFIES SQL DATA
        CALLED ON NULL INPUT
PROCBODY: BEGIN
